    • Class cosc202.andie.ImagePanel

      class ImagePanel extends JPanel implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • image
          cosc202.andie.EditableImage image
          The image to display in the ImagePanel.
        • scale
          double scale

          The zoom-level of the current view. A scale of 1.0 represents actual size; 0.5 is zoomed out to half size; 1.5 is zoomed in to one-and-a-half size; and so forth.

          Note that the scale is internally represented as a multiplier, but externally as a percentage.
